quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  33,55,aurton par apne bapon se ( parda nah karne mein ) kuch gunah nahi aur nah apne biton se aur nah apne bhaiyon se aur nah apne bhtijon se aur nah apne bhanjon se nah apni ( qisam ki ) aurton se aur nah londion se. aur ( ae aurtoo ) khuda se darti raho. be shak khuda har cheez se waaqif hai
  33,56,khuda aur is ke farishtay paighambar par duroood bhaijtay hain. momino tum bhi un par Duroood aur salam bheja karo
  33,57,jo log khuda aur is ke paighambar ko ranj pohanchate hain un par khuda duniya aur akhirat mein laanat karta hai aur un ke liye is ne zaleel karne wala azaab tayyar kar rakha hai
  33,58,aur jo log momin mardon aur momin aurton ko aisay kaam ( ki tohmat se ) jo unhon ne nahkiya ho aeza den to unhon ne bohtan aur Sarih gunah ka boojh apne sir par rakha
  33,59,ae paighambar apni biwion aur baityon aur musalmanoon ki aurton se keh do ke ( bahar nikla karen to ) apne ( monhon ) par chadar latka ( kar ghonghat nikaal ) liya karen. yeh amar un ke liye mojab shanakht ( o imtiaz ) hoga to koi un ko aeza nah day ga. aur khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  33,60,agar munhafiq aur woh log jin ke dilon mein marz hai aur jo madeeney ( ke shehar mein ) buri buri khabrain udaya karte hain ( apne kirdaar ) se baz nah ayen ge to hum tum ko un ke peechay laga den ge phir wahan tumahray paros mein nah reh saken ge magar thoray din
  33,61,( woh bhi ) phatkaray hue. jahan paye gay pakdae gay aur jaan se maar daaley gay
  33,62,jo log pehlay guzar chuke hain un ke baray mein bhi khuda ki yahi aadat rahi hai. aur tum khuda ki aadat mein tagayur o tabdeel nah pao ge
